documentation.description: Trunking client is used to manage resources for Twilio SIP Trunking
Client for managing trunk resources
creates a new trunk resource
defines the input fields for creating a new trunk resource
defines the response fields for the created trunk resource
retrieves a page of trunk resources
defines the response fields for the trunks page
Client for managing a specific trunk resource
Client for managing Origination URL resources
creates a new origination url resource
defines the input fields for creating a new origination url resource
defines the response fields for the created origination url resource
retrieves a page of origination url resources
defines the response fields for the origination urls page
Client for managing a specific origination url resource
retrieves an origination url resource
defines the response fields for the retrieved origination url resource
modifies an origination url resource
defines input fields for updating an origination url resource
defines the response fields for the updated origination url
removes a origination url resource from the account
